	Ukraine)
		title="Гимн Украины"
		music="T78L3BL8BL8BABO5C L3DL8CO4L4BA GBF#B L3EL8F#L4GL4A L3BL8BL8BABO5C L3DL8CO4L4BA GBF#B L2EL4EP4 L3F#L8F#BAGF# EF#GEL4F#L4F# L4GGAA L2BL4BP4 L3F#L8F#BAGF# EF#GEL4F#F# GBF#B L3EL8F#GABO5C O5L3DL8C#L4DO4B AAO5L8DCO4BA L4GGAA L3BL8AGABO5C O5L3DL8C#L4DO4B AAO5L8DCO4BA L4GBF#B O5L2EL3EP8"
